                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>B to Grd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>5 volts &#177; .5</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colspan="2" spanname="S3T4">
                            <para>V Ref. check with key ON, if voltage not in spec., see V Ref circuit.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>C to Grd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>&#60; .25 volts</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colspan="2" spanname="S3T4">
                            <para>If greater than 0.25 volts signal wire is shorted to V Ref of battery.</para>
