                            <para>14.8</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>10.0</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Minimum back pressure signal expected at 2300 rpm (See EPR diagnostics)</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colspan="4" spanname="S1T4">
                            <para>Fault Code Descriptions</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colspan="4" spanname="S1T4">
                            <para>341 = Signal voltage was less than .039 volts for more than 0.1 seconds.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colspan="4" spanname="S1T4">
                            <para>342 = Signal voltage was greater than 4.90 volts for more than 0.1 seconds.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colspan="4" spanname="S1T4">
                            <para>344 = Signal above 1.34 volts with engine off. 19 psi (130 kPa).</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
